msgid "Cauldron"
msgstr "Kaldrono"

msgid "Stores water"
msgstr "Ĝi stokas akvon"

msgid "Cauldrons are used to store water and slowly fill up under rain."
msgstr ""

msgid "Place a water bucket into the cauldron to fill it with water. Place an empty bucket on a full cauldron to retrieve the water. Place a water bottle into the cauldron to fill the cauldron to one third with water. Place a glass bottle in a cauldron with water to retrieve one third of the water."
msgstr ""

